text: Can I come in? Are you okay?

Yeah. It's for when you finish the snow rabbit, right?
It's going to be late, so I thought it might come in handy.
Looking forward to your work, Sensei?

Wow, that's a nice thing to say!
I thought you were going to pelt me with snowballs!

Haha, no, no. Your work is precious enough
that I'd even consider storing it in the freezer.
